2.1 Traffic Data Collection To provide the APP, we will automatically track and collect the following categories of information when you use the APP:
(i) the IP address;
(ii) Domain servers;
(iii) other information related to your device, your device's interaction with the APP and the Application (collectively, 'Traffic Data').
2.2 Personal Information Collected We may ask you to provide us with certain personal information about you ('Personal Information') in order to provide the Applications. Personal information includes the following information categories:
(i) contact data (such as your email address, telephone number and any details of your contact details);
(ii) demographic data (such as your time zone, your postal address and location details); If you communicate with us via email or letter, Phoenix Game may collect any information you provide in such communication.
(iii) financial information (e.g. account details, electronic wallet details, credit or debit card details, etc., which you provided to us for the issuance of prizes and coupons)
2.3 Our Apps may transfer your personal information to our internal servers. Once you delete the application, this personal information will be deleted immediately, unless storage of this personal information is necessary under applicable law. In addition, we have implemented commercially reasonable physical, managerial, operational and technical security measures to protect and secure the loss, misuse and alteration of personal information held by us. Finally, this information is used strictly for our business purposes and to provide you with useful functionality.
2.4 Our Apps may contain links to third party websites or applications. You agree and understand that the privacy policies of these sites are not under our control. You understand that once you leave our servers, the use of any information you provide will be governed by the privacy policies of the website operators you use.
